{"MISRAISE":[{"def":"To raise or exite unreasonable.","pos":""}],"MISRATE":[{"def":"To rate erroneously.","pos":""}],"MISREAD":[{"def":"To read amiss; to misunderstand in reading.","pos":""}],"MISRECEIVE":[{"def":"To receive wrongly.","pos":""}],"MISRECITAL":[{"def":"An inaccurate recital.","pos":""}],"MISRECITE":[{"def":"To recite erroneously.","pos":""}],"MISRECKON":[{"def":"To reckon wrongly; to miscalculate.","pos":""}],"MISRECKONING":[{"def":"An erroneous computation.","pos":""}],"MISRECOLLECT":[{"def":"To have an erroneous remembrance of; to suppose erroneously that one recollects.","pos":""}],"MISRECOLLECTION":[{"def":"Erroneous or inaccurate recollection.","pos":""}],"MISREFORM":[{"def":"To reform wrongly or imperfectly.","pos":""}],"MISREGARD":[{"def":"Wrong understanding; misconstruction.","pos":""}],"MISREGULATE":[{"def":"To regulate wrongly or imperfectly; to fail to regulate.","pos":""}],"MISREHEARSE":[{"def":"To rehearse or quote incorrectly.","pos":""}],"MISRELATE":[{"def":"To relate inaccurately.","pos":""}],"MISRELATION":[{"def":"Erroneous relation or narration.","pos":""}],"MISREMEMBER":[{"def":"To mistake in remembering; not to remember correctly.","pos":""}],"MISRENDER":[{"def":"To render wrongly; to translate or recite wrongly.","pos":""}],"MISREPEAT":[{"def":"To repeat wrongly; to give a wrong version of.","pos":""}],"MISREPORT":[{"def":"To report erroneously; to give an incorrect account of.","pos":""}],"MISREPRESENT":[{"def":"To represent incorrectly (almost always, unfacorably); to give a false erroneous representation of, either maliciously, ignirantly, or carelessly.","pos":""}],"MISREPRESENTATION":[{"def":"Untrue representation; false or incorrect statement or account; -- usually unfavorable to the thing represented; as, a misrepresentation of a person's motives.","pos":""}],"MISREPRESENTATIVE":[{"def":"Tending to convey a wrong impression; misrepresenting.","pos":""}],"MISREPRESENTER":[{"def":"One who misrepresents.","pos":""}],"MISREPUTE":[{"def":"To have in wrong estimation; to repute or estimate erroneously.","pos":""}],"MISRULE":[{"def":"To rule badly; to misgovern.","pos":""}]}